{"tid":1811082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] MOMO 仆街","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T08:37:58.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"65ec4259252f0f9c23010e5d4abe748122e5157b","tid":1811082,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE出席今（4日）晚間金唱片音源部門頒獎典禮，奪下本賞時不但呼喊正在休養中的成員Mina，子瑜更沒來由告白JYP社長，讓成員當場笑翻！然而表演似乎出問題，當成員在中間熱舞時不斷發生腳滑的驚險場面，MOMO甚至直接摔倒、用手扶地，讓觀眾都替她們捏冷汗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4625/d4625250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4625%2Fd4625250.jpg&h=104c1a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE得獎呼喊Mina。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE獲得當晚音源本賞殊榮時，志效代表致詞，祝福大家新的一年都能健健康康，接著還呼喊著遠方的隊友Mina，「Mina啊！我們得獎囉！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4625/d4625251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4625%2Fd4625251.jpg&h=dce61aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜領獎失控告白，成員在旁邊都笑翻。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<br />\n而這時子瑜突然接下麥克風，用韓文說，「我們想要告白公司的朴軫永製作人...」突如其來的舉動似乎成員都不知道，眼見志效、Sana與娜璉在旁邊睜大眼睛，當子瑜說出，「對我們JYP把...拔（爸爸）說一聲我們愛你」，鏡頭拍到三人當場笑慘了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4625/d4625252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4625%2Fd4625252.jpg&h=52691d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE表演時，鏡頭拍到時MOMO已經摔倒敬業爬起。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<br />\n接著TWICE搭乘著旋轉木馬表演《YES or YES》，移動到主舞台表演《Fancy》時，觀眾都可清楚看見，成員們雖然一邊跳舞、一邊唱歌，視線卻不時不時地看著地下，有一幕更明顯看見Sana在飄移。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而擅長跳舞的MOMO平常舞動力道就很大，沒想到下一個鏡頭就發現她跌倒了，疑似滑倒用手扶地，正在從地上爬起來，但還是十分鎮定地回到隊形之中。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不曉得是舞台太滑，還是鞋子出問題，MOMO一直站不穩快跌倒，有一幕更是由定延牽起她的手，讓她安穩的回到舞台中間。而Sana與志效甚至直接折彎腳，想要檢查是否是鞋底出問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4625/d4625269.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4625%2Fd4625269.jpg&h=368e3dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Sana（上圖後左二）與志效（下圖左三）直接彎腳檢查是不是鞋底出問題。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4625/d4625273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4625%2Fd4625273.jpg&h=b035355d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88fce225f005a4df025be5cbb54de00e2165962f","tid":1811082,"uid":240447,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"俾希澈屌到企都冇力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d691b9c7e7ae8c42e6ff77810f3850a52916fe88","tid":1811082,"uid":14739,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"比人屌到腳仔軟"},{"pid":"c100e4a3d09cb72d7a3a0deb07891c5d4a725282","tid":1811082,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"金希切斷腳代打狗"},{"pid":"fa13b061cc37bff89fe712bdec138c80be814b17","tid":1811082,"uid":43061,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"有左又扮左<br />\n遲d又學牙病咁扮有驚恐症"},{"pid":"8be8b9bc3b135aae7b73dc7644178f9a04333a6a","tid":1811082,"uid":165368,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"好學唔學學人假仆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1932603db095c5008695d0f6746f71016472542f","tid":1811082,"uid":7878,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8be8b9bc3b135aae7b73dc7644178f9a04333a6a","tid":1811082,"uid":165368,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"好學唔學學人假仆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"一陣又走唔出個陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6e95a54c52697272a63b9c3bdb2920b361a84d","tid":1811082,"uid":263783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"我知點解 得momo跌<br />\n希徹啲嘢係鞋底所以sin"},{"p